V0153_01_00_01_0.text: Wait 'til you see my Flame Deck in action!

V0153_01_00_02_0.text: I will successfully complete this mission.

V0153_01_00_03_0.text: I just need to stay calm to make the right decisions.

V0153_01_00_04_0.text:
This isn't practice!
This is war!
So Duel like it!

V0153_01_00_05_0.text: I made it this far because my friends believe in me.

V0153_01_00_06_0.text: Jaden, I won't let evil take over your soul!

V0153_03_00_00_0.text: This mission will soon be over.

V0153_03_00_01_0.text: You think those tactics will work against me?

V0153_03_00_04_0.text: I still have plenty of counterstrategies!

V0153_03_00_05_0.text: I have to clear my mind and focus.

V0153_05_00_00_0.text: The whole Duel depends on this draw...

V0153_06_01_02_0.text: You sure you want to do that?

V0153_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0153_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Blaze Accelerator!

V0153_08_00_01_1.text: I fire a Pyro with 500 or lower ATK to destroy your monster!

V0153_08_00_02_1.text:
I'm loadin' up a monster!
Aaand fire!

V0153_08_00_03_0.text: I upgrade Blaze Accelerator into Tri-Blaze Accelerator!

V0153_08_00_04_1.text: It fires a Pyro to destroy your monster and deal you damage!

V0153_08_00_05_1.text:
I load a monster!
Now fire away!

V0153_08_00_06_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Wild Fire!

V0153_08_00_07_0.text: Wild Fire erases Blaze Accelerator to destroy all monsters!

V0153_08_00_07_1.text: Then it Special Summons a Wild Fire Token!

V0153_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Soul of Fire!

V0153_08_00_08_1.text: You get to draw a card, but I get to deal you damage!

V0153_08_00_09_0.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Burial from a Different Dimension!

V0153_08_00_09_1.text: It returns 3 banished monsters to the Graveyard!

V0153_08_00_10_0.text: A true leader takes on all the risks!

V0153_08_00_11_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Blaze Accelerator Reload!

V0153_08_00_12_1.text: By discarding one Volcanic card, I draw a card from my deck!

V0153_08_00_13_0.text: I banish Blaze Accelerator Reload from my Graveyard!

V0153_08_00_13_1.text: That causes a Volcanic in my deck to go to the Graveyard!

V0153_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Volcanic Recharge!

V0153_08_00_14_1.text: Return up to 3 Volcanic monsters in my Graveyard to my deck!

V0153_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Firewall!

V0153_08_00_16_0.text:
That won't work!
I activate Firewall's effect!

V0153_08_00_16_1.text: I banish a Pyro from my Graveyard to cancel your attack!

V0153_08_00_18_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Backfire!

V0153_08_00_20_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Volcanic Wall!

V0153_09_00_00_0.text: When Fire Trooper is summoned, its effect kicks in!

V0153_09_00_00_1.text: I send it to the Graveyard to deal you damage!

V0153_09_00_01_1.text: For every FIRE monster I banish, I destroy a Spell or Trap!

V0153_09_00_02_0.text: Volcanic Shell's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0153_09_00_02_1.text: I pay 500 LP to add a Volcanic Shell in my deck to my hand!

V0153_09_00_03_0.text: Volcanic Scattershot went to the Grave, so you take damage!

V0153_09_00_04_0.text: I fire 2 Volcanic Scattershots to destroy all your monsters!

V0153_09_00_05_0.text: When Volcanic Blaster is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0153_09_00_06_0.text: I already have my final plan in motion!

V0153_09_00_06_1.text: The Volcanic Counter in my Graveyard deals you damage!

V0153_09_00_07_0.text: Volcanic Rocket adds a Blaze Accelerator to my hand!

V0153_09_00_08_1.text: You take damage, but this card can't attack this turn.

V0153_09_00_09_1.text: In exchange for attacking this turn, it deals you damage!

V0153_09_00_10_1.text: I send a card on my field to the Graveyard to deal damage!

V0153_09_00_11_0.text: To keep Volcanic Queen in play, I'll Tribute...

V0153_09_00_14_1.text: The card it targets can't activate!

V0153_09_00_15_0.text: I banish 3 monsters from my Graveyard to Special Summon!

V0153_09_00_16_0.text: The Blazing Mars activates its effect!

V0153_09_00_16_1.text: It sends my other monsters to the Graveyard to deal damage!

V0153_09_00_17_1.text: I return 4 Pyros in my Graveyard to my deck to draw 2 cards!

V0153_09_00_18_0.text: When The Thing in the Crater is beat, its effect activates!

V0153_09_00_18_1.text: I can Special Summon a Pyro monster from my hand!

V0153_09_00_19_0.text: Gaia Soul the Combustible Collective's effect activates!

V0153_09_00_19_1.text: I Tribute Pyro monsters to increase its ATK!

V0153_09_00_20_0.text: Gaia Soul is destroyed during the End Phase.

V0153_09_00_21_0.text: Solar Flare Dragon deals you damage during this End Phase!

V0153_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0153_13_00_11_0.text:
This monster...
It reminds me of...
Mom?

V0153_13_00_12_0.text: Witness the full firepower of my Volcanic Burn Deck!

V0153_13_00_14_0.text: You're a reminder that there's still a Duelist inside me!

V0153_13_00_15_0.text: You have the power to drown the field!

V0153_13_00_19_0.text:
Come on out!
Royal Firestorm Guards!

V0153_13_00_23_0.text: I Special Summon a Wild Fire Token!

V0153_19_00_13_0.text: I'm counting on you, Dancing Fairy!

V0153_19_00_17_0.text: The Thing in the Crater attacks!

V0153_19_00_18_0.text: Gaia Soul the Combustible Collective attacks!

V0153_28_00_01_0.text: You need to increase your firepower if you want to beat me.

V0153_28_00_02_0.text: When you play with me, you're playing with fire!

V0153_28_00_03_0.text: You're not ready to fight on the front lines.

V0153_28_00_04_0.text: I forgot to stay calm and alert.

V0153_28_00_04_1.text: Only you can make me lose my cool.

V0153_28_00_05_0.text: Defeat the darkness and rid yourself of your terror!

V0153_28_00_06_0.text:
It's lonely to live in the shadows.
Believe me, I know.

V0153_29_00_00_0.text: Your tactics were superior to mine.

V0153_29_00_01_0.text:
You dodged a bullet.
If only I didn't lose my cool...

V0153_29_00_02_0.text:
I was overconfident.
I won't make this mistake again.

V0153_29_00_03_0.text: I've fought many opponents, but none as tough as you.

V0153_29_00_04_0.text: You're easy to figure out, but hard to defeat.

V0153_29_00_05_0.text: Jaden, thanks for reminding me what my father taught me.

V0153_33_00_00_0.text: My Flame Deck torches everyone it faces!

V0153_33_00_01_0.text: I'll lead my troops into battle!

V0153_33_00_02_0.text: I'll use this strategy to outflank you!

V0153_30_00_00_0.text: Are you trying to overwhelm me?

V0153_30_00_01_0.text: This card may be a decoy.

V0153_34_00_02_0.text: Time to dig in and take a stand!

V0153_34_00_03_0.text: Is there nothing I can do but lose?

V0153_34_00_06_0.text: I hope we meet again under better circumstances.
